309
00:16:14,039 --> 00:16:16,559
But yeah, it's a very interesting job.

310
00:16:16,799 --> 00:16:17,940
I think it would be very lonely.

311
00:16:18,279 --> 00:16:23,159
And also I think, well, now maybe that's been reduced a lot because now you have the internet.

312
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:29,679
Oh yeah, well the internet means that the salespeople come to you without you having to get up.

313
00:16:29,679 --> 00:16:34,580
So basically you're sitting at home in your pajamas and you can order a TV and some clothes.

314
00:16:34,740 --> 00:16:38,980
But it's very interesting because I remember you would have all these door-to-door sales.

315
00:16:39,139 --> 00:16:43,320
